---
import Base from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<Base title="Ball Mill Grind Size Optimizer">

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Ball Mill Grind Size Optimizer</h1>
  <p class="sub">
    Production-grade time series ML system for stabilizing grind size and improving energy efficiency in mining operations.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="grid">
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Problem</h3>
    <p>
      Grinding circuits experienced unstable grind size distribution causing throughput loss, downstream flotation inefficiency,
      and excessive energy consumption.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3>Data</h3>
    <p>
      High-frequency PI Vision sensor streams: specific energy, tonnage, particle size, water flow, mill load and power draw.
    </p>
  </div>

  <section class="architecture">
    <h2>System Architecture</h2>

    <svg viewBox="0 0 900 420" class="diagram">

      <!-- Data Sources -->
      <rect x="40" y="160" width="180" height="70" rx="14"/>
      <text x="130" y="200">PI Vision Sensors</text>

      <!-- ETL -->
      <rect x="270" y="160" width="180" height="70" rx="14"/>
      <text x="360" y="200">Snowflake ETL</text>

      <!-- ML -->
      <rect x="500" y="140" width="220" height="100" rx="18"/>
      <text x="610" y="185">ML Inference Engine</text>

      <!-- UI -->
      <rect x="760" y="160" width="120" height="70" rx="14"/>
      <text x="820" y="200">Operator UI</text>

      <!-- Flow Lines -->
      <path d="M220 195 H270" />
      <path d="M450 195 H500" />
      <path d="M720 195 H760" />

    </svg>
  </section>

  <div class="card">
    <h3>Model</h3>
    <p>
      Multivariate time-series regression models trained to predict grind size target windows based on real-time specific energy behavior.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3>Pipeline</h3>
    <p>
      Snowflake → Feature Engineering → Model Inference → Bound Enforcement → Operator Dashboard → Alarm & Control Loop
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3>Deployment</h3>
    <p>
      Containerized ML inference services deployed in internal cloud infrastructure with CI/CD and monitoring.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3>Business Impact</h3>
    <p>
      Improved grind stability, reduced downstream reprocessing, and enabled proactive energy optimization.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="lessons card">
  <h3>Engineering Lessons</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Noise-aware bound enforcement prevents oscillatory operator behavior</li>
    <li>Time-series drift monitoring is critical in mineral variability</li>
    <li>Operator-facing dashboards drive adoption more than raw model accuracy</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<style>
.hero{max-width:var(--max);margin:auto;text-align:center}
.sub{color:var(--muted)}
.lessons ul{padding-left:1.2rem}
</style>

</Base>
